<text>Interstate 235 is the designation for three Interstate Highways in the United States, all of which are related to Interstate 35:
*Interstate 235 (Iowa), an east–west route through downtown Des Moines.
*Interstate 235 (Kansas), a bypass route of Interstate 135 that travels around the western part of Wichita.
*Interstate 235 (Oklahoma), a long north–south route from downtown to north-central Oklahoma City.</text><links>
