<doc id="489795" wikidata="Q5418603" url="?curid=489795" title="Evolution (Twins album)">
<text>Evolution (進化論), is the eighth album of Twins and was released September 2003. The disc contains 10 songs.

==CD content==
#&quot;Luan Shi Jia Ren&quot; (亂世佳人)
#&quot;Ni Jiang Ni Ai Wo&quot; (你講你愛我)
#&quot;Huang Xin Jia Qi&quot; (慌心假期)
#&quot;You Know What I Mean&quot;
#&quot;Peng YOu De Ai&quot; (朋友的愛)
#&quot;Xia Ru Kuang Hua&quot; (夏日狂嘩)
#&quot;Gao Wen Yu Jia&quot; (高溫瑜伽)
#&quot;Xiang Gang Niu Yue&quot; (香港紐約)
#&quot;Beautiful Day&quot;
#&quot;San Jiao Yuan Wu&quot; (三角圓舞)</text><links>
